(X, \mathcal F, \mu)
f\in M^+(X,\mu)
t>0
S_f(t)=\{x\in X:f(x)>t\} \quad \Psi_f(t)=\mu(S_f(t))
\int_Xfd\mu=\int_0^\infty \Psi_f(t)dt
\{f_n\}_{n=0}^\infty
f:f\in M^+ \land \lim_{n\to \infty}\int_Xf_nd\mu=\int_Xfd\mu
